557
00:27:21,793 --> 00:27:23,827
You are sausages here!

558
00:27:23,827 --> 00:27:25,827
Ignorant sausages!

559
00:27:25,827 --> 00:27:27,655
- I think you mean "savages."

560
00:27:27,655 --> 00:27:28,862
- I don't care, I go!

561
00:27:28,862 --> 00:27:29,620
Hate you savages!

562
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:33,000
