glue will do you.

602
00:30:02,310 --> 00:30:03,034
- [Suzie] Magic glue.

603
00:30:04,689 --> 00:30:05,206
- Dear.

604
00:30:07,793 --> 00:30:09,000
- [Suzie] And.

